data.description: Don’t miss the opportunity to own this spacious, ready to move-in 1 bedroom, 1 bath condo located in the prime community of Woodlake Towers Condo in Falls Church, Second Floor unit with fresh paint, vinyl plank flooring.  Peace of mind with utility bills - water, sewer, electricity, and gas all included in the Condo Fee. Washers and dryers are conveniently located on each floor. Patio perfect for enjoying morning coffee, evening relaxation and cookouts. The building also has a fitness center, Sauna, a party hall, swimming pools, tennis court, playground, gazebos for cookouts, and convenience store.  Great location, close to DC, Arlington, shops and dining. You’re within minutes of essential amenities, shopping, dining, and excellent transportation options.  Bus stop less than a mile, easy commuting. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort that this condo has to offer!
